last_episode_to_air.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Goodbye
last_episode_to_air.overview: Zoey must face a difficult goodbye.

name: Zoey's Extraordinary Playlist
overview: After an unusual event, Zoey Clarke, a whip-smart computer coder forging her way in San Francisco, suddenly starts to hear the innermost wants, thoughts and desires of the people around her through popular songs.
tagline: She can hear the soundtrack of your life.

episodes.name: Pilot
episodes.overview: A young woman discovers she has the ability to hear the innermost thoughts of people around her as songs and musical numbers.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Best Friend
episodes.overview: Zoey tries to figure out how to control her new abilities while navigating her best friends’ romantic feelings for her. A new medical victory for Mitch gives the family hope.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Boss
episodes.overview: Zoey must decide whether or not to get involved in her boss Joan's troubled marriage after she hears Joan sing a heart song. Also, Zoey creates a new program for the family to communicate with Mitch, but his first word is not what they expected.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Neighbor
episodes.overview: Zoey is forced to address her own faith and why she was given these powers as she attempts to help Mo feel comfortable expressing his true self. David creates a “big moment” for Mitch.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Failure
episodes.overview: After hearing her first duet, Zoey gets a little too involved in her brother's marriage. Leif receives negative feedback at work. Maggie is offered an enticing work opportunity.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Night Out
episodes.overview: Things get complicated for Zoey at Simon's engagement party. Maggie has a night out alone, but it doesn't go as planned.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Confession
episodes.overview: Zoey is forced to admit some hard truths to Max. Tobin worries his friendship with Leif is on the rocks. Mo struggles to communicate with the new man in his life.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Glitch
episodes.overview: After receiving heartbreaking news, Zoey suffers a mysterious “glitch” in her powers.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Silence
episodes.overview: Zoey tries to help Mitch’s caregiver, Howie, reconnect with his estranged daughter. Max must make a decision about his future at SPRQ Point.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Outburst
episodes.overview: Zoey surprisingly finds herself getting into major conflict with Simon, Max, Mo and even Howie. Tensions arise at SPRQ Point when the fourth and sixth floors compete over an important piece of code. Mitch and Maggie try to celebrate their anniversary.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Mother
episodes.overview: Zoey has to figure out a clever way to help her mother with an impossible decision. Max unexpectedly bonds with Leif. Mo hits a rough-patch with Eddie.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Dad
episodes.overview: After hearing an ominous song, Zoey does everything in her power to stop something bad from happening.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Return
episodes.overview: Zoey returns to the world after an extended time away and discovers that a lot has changed at work and in her personal life in her absence.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Distraction
episodes.overview: Zoey's attempts to spend private time with Max are continually thwarted by both Mo and work problems. The Clarke family gets a new guest when Emily's sister, Jenna, comes to "help" with the baby.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Dreams
episodes.overview: Zoey is haunted by bad dreams that start to affect her personal life. Jenna helps Maggie find her creative spark again.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Employee
episodes.overview: Zoey tries to "choose happiness" but finds it is easier said than done. David re-evaluates his priorities. Mo and Max face their first real challenge as business partners.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Trip
episodes.overview: Zoey decides to explore her rebellious side with her neighbor from growing up, Aiden. Max's dad comes to visit.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Reckoning
episodes.overview: Simon wrestles with his future at SPRQ Point after calling out racial bias at the company. Mo and Max pitch a new investor for their business venture.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Memory
episodes.overview: Zoey's effort to recreate a cherished memory with Mitch is thwarted by Leif. Max and Mo have their big restaurant opening.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Birthday
episodes.overview: It's Zoey's 30th birthday, but before she can celebrate properly she must confront her unresolved feelings for the men in her life.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Mystery
episodes.overview: After going to see a medium, Zoey's powers mysteriously start glitching again.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Girls' Night
episodes.overview: Zoey gets more than she bargained for when she tries to help Emily with a problem. Maggie reconnects with an old friend. Max, Simon and Mo have a bonding night together.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Double Date
episodes.overview: Zoey attempts to throw all her energy into her relationship, but things get complicated when a double date doesn't go as planned.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Session
episodes.overview: In therapy, Zoey reflects back on her unexpectedly profound first day working at SPRQPoint.

episodes.name: Zoey's Extraordinary Goodbye
episodes.overview: Zoey must face a difficult goodbye.
